OL,6,FAs the government works to reduce the
OL,7,Fbacklog of asylum seekers, some
OL,8,Fcouncils say it is creating a "new
OL,9,Fcrisis", with migrants having nowhere
OL,10,Fto go and local government struggling
OL,11,Fto provide suitable accommodation.
OL,13,FPaul Dennett, The Mayor of , says the
OL,14,Fgovernment needs to understand the
OL,15,Fconsequences of their policy.
