OL,3,C'Never seen demand like it', refugee
OL,4,Chomeless problem worse than ever
OL,6,F"People have been given indefinite
OL,7,Fleave to remain here in the United
OL,8,FKingdom and what that then triggers is
OL,9,Fliterally evicting people from their
OL,10,Fhomes and then them turning up to the
OL,11,Flocal authority to be processed under
OL,12,Fthe Homelessness Reduction Act," he
OL,13,Fsaid.
OL,15,F"Here in Salford and across Greater
OL,16,FManchester, we already have a huge
OL,17,Fchallenge with being able to move
OL,18,Fpeople on and we're unable to move
OL,19,Fthem on because of the chronic under-
OL,20,Fsupply of truly affordable housing."
