OL,6,FOn 20 December, Salford council opened
OL,7,Fup its welfare hub to provide help for
OL,8,Fthose struggling to find accommodation
OL,9,Fover the winter months.
OL,11,FIt has spaces available for 40 people,
OL,12,Fmale and female, the majority of whom
OL,13,Fare refugees.
OL,15,FPaul Dennett added: "The government
OL,16,Fsays they want to work with us, well
OL,17,Fcome and see for yourselves the
OL,18,Fconsequences of your decision-making
OL,19,Fbecause this is totally unacceptable
OL,20,Fin one of the richest and wealthiest
OL,21,Fcountries in the world."
