OL,4,Chomeless problem worse than ever
OL,6,FJennifer-Anne Smith, from Loaves and
OL,7,FFishes - a homeless charity in - says
OL,8,Fclearing the backlog has had negative
OL,9,Fknock-on effects.
OL,11,FShe said: "At the moment, the Home
OL,12,FOffice and fast-tracking of refugees
OL,13,Fand asylum seekers has taking us to
OL,14,Fnear breaking-point.
OL,16,F"Our demand is the highest it's ever
OL,17,Fbeen. In December, we recorded our
OL,18,Fhighest ever number."
