OL,6,FOsam, 18, is currently homeless having
OL,7,Fcome to the UK from Sudan when he was
OL,8,Fjust 16. Although he's been given
OL,9,Fleave to remain in this country, he
OL,10,Fhas struggled to find somewhere to
OL,11,Flive, and has been going to Loaves and
OL,12,FFishes for a warm place to eat.
OL,14,F"I don't know how to explain, it's too
OL,15,Fdifficult to me, I'm not happy, I have
OL,16,Fno friends, I feel alone," he said.
